snippet.title: 39 Days to Mars - Xbox One Trailer
snippet.description:
Embark on the 19th century's most unreliable spaceship in this one or two player couch co-op adventure.

Website : http://www.itsanecdotal.com/39days/

39 Days to Mars is a unique game designed to be played with a friend, where both players have important roles in the expedition. Solo players are aided by the computer-controlled ship's cat.

Available now on Xbox One : https://www.microsoft.com/p/39-days-to-mars/9nhd9tbk2m03

--

Music by Chris Zabriskie
